### 4️⃣ DashboardPage.css (Page-Specific Styles Only)

**Add to `DashboardPage.css`:**
- **Page layout** (grid, flex, positioning)
- **Page-specific spacing** and sizing
- **Page-unique sections** styling
- **Responsive breakpoints** for this page

**Do NOT add:**
- Generic component styles (those are in `index.css`)
- Theme toggle styles (those are in `index.css`)
- Reusable patterns

**Example:**

```css
/* src/styles/DashboardPage.css */

/* ======================== */
/* DASHBOARD PAGE SPECIFIC STYLES */
/* ======================== */

/* Dashboard Container */
.dashboard-container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  padding: var(--spacing-lg);
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Dashboard Header */
.dashboard-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
}

.dashboard-header h1 {
  font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
}

/* Stats Grid */
.stats-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--spacing-md);
  margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
}

.stat-card {
  text-align: center;
  padding: var(--spacing-md);
}

.stat-card h3 {
  font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  color: var(--color-primary);
  margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);
}

/* Dashboard Actions */
.dashboard-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--spacing-md);
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
}

.dashboard-actions .btn {
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 150px;
  max-width: 250px;
}

/* ======================== */
/* RESPONSIVE DASHBOARD STYLES */
/* ======================== */

/* Mobile: max-width 480px */
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .dashboard-container {
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .dashboard-actions {
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .dashboard-actions .btn {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
  }
}

/* Tablet: 481px to 768px */
@media (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 768px) {
  .stats-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

/* Desktop: 769px and above */
@media (min-width: 769px) {
  .dashboard-container {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  }
}
```

